{"tid":1585382,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［行山撚］東涌行去大澳","createTime":"2019-09-21T14:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:46:08.000Z","uid":141263,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"06cc5cfac69f0343febbabd1b7c6213538ae42f6","tid":1585382,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"見呢兩日天氣開始冇咁熱，就揀左條簡單d嘅山路行下，慢慢開始行返山。<br />\n<br />\n由東涌行去大澳，東澳古道，行行企企，拍下片，影下相，食下野，行左三個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回程就坐巴士🚌，廢事重複行多轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整左條片分享，好比心機整架，大家入去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-IZmbnii-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-IZmbnii-s&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=b2894dc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-IZmbnii-s</a>"},{"pid":"9bd292ee2e18c521bb66ede786634f998364f526","tid":1585382,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0208572c5643a29a47749061a0668b3780fb3a49","tid":1585382,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6ac07401617c7094680f6ff65b6bbeef927b1e","tid":1585382,"uid":9296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"影得幾好"},{"pid":"047ca8c6808f2cee350d47b50e90ba116d06b8b2","tid":1585382,"uid":210233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"留名待看"},{"pid":"0eef88c8f476a42e85a7cea041d5cb077b6742e2","tid":1585382,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b6ac07401617c7094680f6ff65b6bbeef927b1e","tid":1585382,"uid":9296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0